description: The image provides event information. The event is titled "Exploring Today's Mobile Moment" and features Nestle-Purina, Snapchat, and Mistplay. It is presented by Moloco. The speakers are Beth Berger (Moloco), Diana Gilbert (Nestle-Purina), Jasmine Ye (Snap Inc.), and Noa Gutterman (Mistplay). The event takes place from 10:00 am to 10:20 am in Boulevard Ballroom 159-163, and the "Main" location is highlighted. Moloco, Inc. is the session sponsor. A yellow calendar icon is also visible.
